By default, <%= pne %> automatically creates a new, blank document when it
starts, although this behavior can be changed in
[Preferences][prefs-docappearance].

You can also create a new document by selecting **New** in the	**File** menu.
![file menu](all-menu-file){: .menu_dropshadow}

